                                <div class="boot-line">Memory: 64KB RAM ‚úì</div>
                                <div class="boot-line">Graphics: VDP ‚úì</div>
                                <div class="boot-line">Sound: Enhanced PSG ‚úì</div>
                                <div class="boot-line">Controllers: 2P ‚úì</div>
                                <div class="boot-line">‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê</div>
                                <div class="boot-line">Loading Game Library...</div>
                                <div class="boot-line">Found @(Games.Count) cartridge(s)</div>
                                <div class="boot-line">Audio System: Ready ‚úì</div>
                                <div class="boot-line">‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê</div>
